metadata.name: wrong Angels
metadata.description:
I recommend paying attention to the centre of the picture.The name of the flowers which are located in the middle of the painting is(papaver somneferum, commonly known as a opium poppy).The flowers represent the heavy drugs and the Angels are demonstrating the people who are strongly addicted to narcotics.The problem is that, these people do not accept themselves as a drug addicted and the blood coming out of her leg is actually showing us that their life is ending.
